{"word":"G757 - ἄρχω - árchō - ar'-kho - Reign over","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄρχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">árchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ar'-kho</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Reign over</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆளு"},{"paragraph":"1. to be the first to do (anything), to begin"},{"paragraph":"2. to be chief, leader, ruler"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to be <i>first</i> (in political rank or power): - reign (rule) over.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G536/536\">G536</a>, <a href=\"#/G744/744\">G744</a>, <a href=\"#/G746/746\">G746</a>, <a href=\"#/G747/747\">G747</a>, <a href=\"#/G757/757\">G757</a>, <a href=\"#/G758/758\">G758</a>"}]}